                          "@BorderLeft": "solid",
                          "@BorderRight": "solid",
                          "@BorderTop": "solid",
                          "Sentence": {
                            "@WritingMode": "vertical",
                            "#text": "政令で定める者"
                          }
                        },
                        {
                          "@BorderBottom": "solid",
                          "@BorderLeft": "solid",
                          "@BorderRight": "solid",
                          "@BorderTop": "solid",
                          "Sentence": {
                            "@WritingMode": "vertical",
                            "#text": "政令で定める額"
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "TableColumn": [
                        {
                          "@BorderBottom": "solid",
                          "@BorderLeft": "solid",
                          "@BorderRight": "solid",
                          "@BorderTop": "solid",
                          "Sentence": {
                            "@WritingMode": "vertical",
                            "#text": "一　警備業務の種別（法第十八条に規定する種別をいう。以下この条において同じ。）のうち、法第二条第一項第一号に掲げる警備業務に係るものに係る検定（法第二十三条第一項に規定する検定をいう。以下この条において同じ。）を受けようとする者"
                          }
                        },
                        {
                          "@BorderBottom": "solid",
                          "@BorderLeft": "solid",
                          "@BorderRight": "solid",
                          "@BorderTop": "solid",
                          "Sentence": {
                            "@WritingMode": "vertical",
                            "#text": "一万六千円"
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "TableColumn": [
                        {
                          "@BorderBottom": "solid",
                          "@BorderLeft": "solid",
                          "@BorderRight": "solid",
                          "@BorderTop": "solid",
                          "Sentence": {
                            "@WritingMode": "vertical",
                            "#text": "二　警備業務の種別のうち、法第二条第一項第二号に掲げる警備業務に係るものに係る検定（国家公安委員会規則で定める車両その他の機材を用いて行われるものに限る。）を受けようとする者"
                          }
                        },
                        {
                          "@BorderBottom": "solid",
                          "@BorderLeft": "solid",
                          "@BorderRight": "solid",
                          "@BorderTop": "solid",
                          "Sentence": {
                            "@WritingMode": "vertical",
                            "#text": "一万四千円"
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "TableColumn": [
                        {
                          "@BorderBottom": "solid",
                          "@BorderLeft": "solid",
                          "@BorderRight": "solid",
                          "@BorderTop": "solid",
                          "Sentence": {
                            "@WritingMode": "vertical",
                            "#text": "三　警備業務の種別のうち、法第二条第一項第二号に掲げる警備業務に係るものに係る検定（前号に規定するものを除く。）を受けようとする者"
                          }
                        },
                        {
                          "@BorderBottom": "solid",
                          "@BorderLeft": "solid",
                          "@BorderRight": "solid",
                          "@BorderTop": "solid",
                          "Sentence": {
                            "@WritingMode": "vertical",
                            "#text": "一万三千円"
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "TableColumn": [
                        {
                          "@BorderBottom": "solid",
                          "@BorderLeft": "solid",
                          "@BorderRight": "solid",
                          "@BorderTop": "solid",
                          "Sentence": {
                            "@WritingMode": "vertical",
                            "#text": "四　警備業務の種別のうち、法第二条第一項第三号に掲げる警備業務に係るものに係る検定を受けようとする者"
                          }
                        },
                        {
                          "@BorderBottom": "solid",
                          "@BorderLeft": "solid",
                          "@BorderRight": "solid",
                          "@BorderTop": "solid",
                          "Sentence": {
                            "@WritingMode": "vertical",
                            "#text": "一万六千円"
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "TableColumn": [
                        {
                          "@BorderBottom": "solid",
                          "@BorderLeft": "solid",
                          "@BorderRight": "solid",
                          "@BorderTop": "solid",
                          "Sentence": {
                            "@WritingMode": "vertical",
                            "#text": "五　法第二十三条第四項に規定する合格証明書（以下この条において単に「合格証明書」という。）の交付を受けようとする者"
                          }
                        },
                        {
                          "@BorderBottom": "solid",
                          "@BorderLeft": "solid",
                          "@BorderRight": "solid",
                          "@BorderTop": "solid",
                          "Sentence": {
                            "@WritingMode": "vertical",
                            "#text": "一万円"
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "TableColumn": [
                        {
                          "@BorderBottom": "solid",
                          "@BorderLeft": "solid",
                          "@BorderRight": "solid",
                          "@BorderTop": "solid",
                          "Sentence": {
                            "@WritingMode": "vertical",
                            "#text": "六　合格証明書の書換えを受けようとする者"
                          }
                        },
                        {
                          "@BorderBottom": "solid",
                          "@BorderLeft": "solid",
                          "@BorderRight": "solid",
                          "@BorderTop": "solid",
                          "Sentence": {
                            "@WritingMode": "vertical",
                            "#text": "二千二百円"
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    },
